reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Affordable and stylish

Title: Affordable and Adorable Patio SetRating: ★★★★★I recently purchased this 4-piece patio set, and I couldn't be happier with the value it offers. It's the perfect combination of affordability and charm for any outdoor space.First and foremost, the design is incredibly cute. The set includes two comfortable chairs, a matching loveseat, and a coffee table, all featuring a charming and stylish design that adds a touch of elegance to my patio. The color and finish are pleasing to the eye, and it instantly brightened up my outdoor area.Assembly was a breeze. The set came with clear instructions, and all the necessary tools were included. Within no time, I had the whole set set up and ready to use.Despite its affordability, the build quality is surprisingly good. The materials feel sturdy, and the chairs and loveseat are comfortable to sit in. The cushions included are a nice touch and provide extra comfort.The coffee table is a convenient addition, providing a spot for drinks, snacks, or decorative items. It's just the right size for my needs.While this set may not be as high-end as some more expensive options, it provides excellent value for the price. It's perfect for small gatherings, morning coffee, or simply relaxing in the fresh air.If you're in the market for an affordable patio set that doesn't compromise on style and comfort, this 4-piece patio set is a fantastic choice. It has added a delightful touch to my outdoor space and has become my favorite spot for enjoying the outdoors

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I’d give it 5 stars if it weren’t for the assembly
reviews.reviewText: Literally this is so cute and it’s so reasonably priced that I was like how can I complain about it but the assembly was a literal nightmare and there’s still screws I can’t get in so the whole thing is a little unstable. My fingers are in so much pain from putting this together and everything is a little uneven and wonky - it took me about 3 hours to roughly get it together and again I’m still not fully done with it. I imagine after I finally get it fully put together it’ll be perfect and I’ll never have to deal with those ridiculous screws and Allen wrench again but until then still dealing with the nonsense that is the assembly of this product.That being said I f you don’t mind the frustrating process of putting it together it’s actually really nice. The cushions are a bit thin I imagine I may change those out but the chairs themselves are really great.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Worth it for the price
reviews.reviewText: I’m giving this a 4 star bc for $130 patio set, you can’t beat it. I’ll list the pros and cons belowPROS:Great priceSeems sturdyEasy to piece together although it does take a minuteCushions are comfortable and great material for outdoorsLooks nice with the two chairs we already owned and matches them really closelyCONS:The glass on the table WILL NOT line up and sit flush, no matter how much fidgeting we have done to try and get it to fit. The inside dimension of the table for the space that the glass should fit into is not as wide as the glass itself. Very aggravating but we are going to attempt to place a waterproof wood insert onto it instead since we have a toddler and do not want her to fall and it shatter. Etc.it was a bit time consuming as I mentioned to put together. But that’s part of it.Some of the holes were a bit tricky to line up. We would have to shift the wrapping material out of the way so that the hole would be unconcerned. But not a huge deal. It did not prevent us from being able to screw the screw in after we put a little elbow grease into it.Only 1 chair is not level. One of the feet are shorter then the rest and the bottom of the legs do not screw up or down to adjust for the error. So it has no way to be balanced. It’s only about .5 inch but it was noticeable when we placed it on the concrete. We may just attach a piece of wood or metal to the bottom permanently so it will sit level and not come off if someone moves the chair.Overall though we are very pleased and happy with the outcome. We got our little outdoor rug and the decorations all from Ross and then snagged some plants for the pots at Home Depot. Definitely made our patio much more welcoming and we can wait to host guest this summer for cookouts

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent quality outdoor furniture that's durable and easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: This outdoor furniture exceeded my expectations, earning a well-deserved 5-star rating. Its durability and excellent quality are immediately evident, with sturdy materials that withstand the elements. Everything is super comfortable and my whole family loves it. It's also great for when we have guests over! What sets this furniture apart is its user-friendly installation process. Setting up the pieces was a breeze, thanks to the design and clear instructions. I recommend spending a few dollars and buying the hex bolt attachment for your power drill because I was able to put this together within less than an hour easily. Overall, this furniture is durable, top-notch quality, and easy to install, making it the perfect choice for those seeking affordable outdoor furniture. I highly recommend it!
